data.description: You will not want to miss this charming home with a huge garage that is every homeowner's dream! This home checks all of the boxes, from the gorgeous tall ceilings, tall kitchen cabinets, open floor plan, beautifully tiled showers, covered porch, MASSIVE oversized 4 car garage with oversized garage doors, new carpet, new paint, freshly sealed driveway, new dishwasher and stove, and so much more! All located in the highly desired Roxana School District. Schedule your showing today because this one won't last long!
